Class ResourceID

  • public class ResourceID
extends Object
    The class ResourceID represents a discovery service resource ID. The following schema fragment specifies the expected content within the ResourceID object. 
     <xs:element name="ResourceID" type="ResourceIDType"/>
 <complexType name="ResourceIDType">
   <simpleContent>
     <extension base="<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema>anyURI">
       <attribute name="id" type="{http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema}ID" />
     </extension>
   </simpleContent>
 </complexType>
